<bibRefCitation author="Herman, L. H." box="[1138,1297,643,669]" pageId="2" pageNumber="153" pagination="1 - 4218" refId="ref20353" refString="Herman, L. H. (2001) Catalog of the Staphylinidae (Insecta: Coleoptera). 1758 to the end of the second millennium. Bulletin of the American Museum of Natural History, 265, 1 - 4218. https: // doi. org / 10.1206 / 0003 - 0090.265.1.1" type="journal article" year="2001">Herman 2001</bibRefCitation>
